    h4#College College of Science
    p.lead
      | Sungkyunkwan University College of Science is one of the fastest growing universities in the field of basic science in Korea. The College of Science is attempting a special educational program to adopt innovative and original teaching methods to cultivate excellent scientific talents and produce global scientists in basic science.
