          tr
            td  - Chemistry 
    h4#Information College of Information and Communication Engineering
    p.lead
      | To respond to the ever-changing needs in national informatization and the ICT industry, the College of Information and Communication Engineering runs various research and educational programs to foster and develop ICT professionals, leveraging its outstanding faculty and state-of-the-art facility.
