    h4#Biotechnology College of Biotechnology and Bioengineering
    p.lead
      | Bioengineering technology (BT) in the 21st century is an important field of national growth engines along with IT and nanotechnology (NT). College of Biotechnology and Bioengineering has educational programs that can train students combining BT, IT, and NT within its faculty. The 600-year history of Sungkyunkwan University College of Biotechnology and Bioengineering aims to foster global leaders with creativity and initiative based on the educational ideology of the academic community.
