    h4#Sport College of Sport Science  
    p.lead
      | The College of Sport Science aims to foster future talent who can actively cope with rapidly changing social and personal living conditions. Under the belief that a healthy society can be realized by a healthy body and a people with a healthy mind, the college has goals to grow future sports leaders, focusing on wisdom, virtue and healthy body.
