    h4#Medicine School of Medicine
    p.lead
      | School of Medicine was established in 1997. The school aims to educate doctors who can provide best treatment for the patients, design creative research projects, and serve the community with social responsibility. The School of Medicine provides students with 1 on 1 intensive learning environment along with the state-of-the-art clinical training facilities. Top-tier faculty members and training hospitals enables students to become competent medical scientists in the era of artificial intelligence. Despite its short history, SKKU School of Medicine now stands as the one of the top medical schools in Korea, and aims to become one of the leading medical schools in the world.
